# Nzaka Portfolio Website

Welcome to my personal portfolio website! This is a showcase of my journey as an aspiring web developer, highlighting my skills, projects, and passion for creating user-friendly websites.

## 🌟 Features
- **About Me**: Learn more about my background and skills.
- **Projects**: Explore some of my latest work.
- **Recipes**: Check out my favorite dishes with step-by-step guides.
- **Responsive Design**: Fully optimized for all devices.

## 🛠 Technologies Used
- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript

## 📁 Project Structure
```
Nzaka-Portfolio/
│
├── index.html       # Main landing page
├── style.css        # Styling for the website
├── images/          # Contains all media assets
│   ├── profile.jpg
│   ├── recipe1.jpg
│   ├── recipe2.jpg
│
└── README.md        # Project documentation
```

## 🚀 Getting Started
To run this project locally:
1. Clone the repository:
   ```sh
   git clone https://github.com/Nzaka05/portfolio.git
   ```
2. Open `index.html` in your preferred browser.

